{"tid":2355340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女警涉洗黑錢提堂 沒親友協助未能交出保釋金 要求出去撳機 杜浩成批准","createTime":"2021-01-06T05:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T07:18:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":58,"dislike":308,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9dd766946fe6085709ee0e2de2a540bc1baa1a","tid":2355340,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"再有警隊人員涉嫌知法犯法。隸屬東區刑事調查隊的女警涉嫌於2019至2020年間洗黑錢，涉款共逾53萬元。她上月被拘控兩罪，案件今早於觀塘裁判法院提堂。辯方要求暫緩答辯，裁判官杜浩成一度下令將涉案女警還柙，直至她交出一萬元現金保釋才可離開；及後代表律師要求讓被告「出去撳機」，杜官最終批准她先行外出，24小時內交出保釋金。<br />\n<br />\n杜官同意將案件押後至3月1日答辯，但下令還押被告，直至她交出一萬元保釋金。代表律師隨即表示沒有其他人能協助被告，要求法庭讓被告「出去撳機」。杜官接納要求，改為被告於24小時內交出保釋金便可。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210106/K5GK5FTN2NB35CQUKAULA7OQ6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210106%2FK5GK5FTN2NB35CQUKAULA7OQ6U%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=a1e00128\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210106%2FK5GK5FTN2NB35CQUKAULA7OQ6U%2F&h=20445aed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210106/K5GK5FTN2NB35CQUKAULA7OQ6U/</a>"},{"pid":"a58dca15354620f77f125e9e318a35ea2c841861","tid":2355340,"uid":53498,"like":166,"dislike":0,"score":166,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"嗰一皮都係黑錢嚟,狗官係共犯"},{"pid":"e4247e0fb19e73d41c18ea1c4f017861043e1b6a","tid":2355340,"uid":130438,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"佢洗得太早<br />\n如果遲多些少再洗<br />\n根本拉都唔會拉"},{"pid":"36d321859258dbaa2ec112e525ac21e2789bf984","tid":2355340,"uid":117301,"like":208,"dislike":0,"score":208,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"份工做到連親友都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a2e806674ca57c4ed1a469c761f99504e13786","tid":2355340,"uid":32511,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:14:53.000Z","m